A '''vidmap''' was a wall-mounted, two-dimensional map. A vidmap of [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] was aboard the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]] ship [[Admiral Ackbar (Victory-class)|''Admiral Ackbar'']]. Smaller versions were enclosed within helmets as a head-up display.<ref name="tempest">''[[Legacy of the Force: Tempest]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Vidmaps first appeared in the book ''[[Tatooine Ghost]]''.

==Appearances==
*''[[Tatooine Ghost]]'' {{1st}}
*''[[Legacy of the Force: Tempest]]''

